{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_03_01",
  "title": "白石千紗 1話 ソロパートに挑戦",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……1、2、3、4……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4……1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7500,
          "startTime": 8.4666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7500,
          "startTime": 8.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs001-02.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user} san‚ thank you for your help!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、一人で自主練してたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job‚ were you working on your own?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、もうすぐライブバトルなので\n本番までに振り付けを完璧にしておきたくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it's almost time for the live battle\nand I wanted to make sure the choreography was perfect before the show…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "入所した頃は体力がなくてダンスも苦手だったのに\n千紗も成長したな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa has grown up so much‚ even though she wasn't very strong\nand bad at dancing when she first joined us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、嬉しいです\n最近はダンスを重点的に練習してるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ I'm glad.\nI've been practicing dance a lot lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "この間なんて怜ちゃんからも\nダンスがうまくなったって褒められたんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other day‚ Rei-chan complimented me\non my dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.51,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんにはレッスン中によく叱られてたから\n私も成長してるんだって思えて嬉しかったなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan used to scold me a lot during the lessons‚\nso I was happy to see that I was growing up too. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば以前、怜から相談を受けたことがあったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ Rei once asked me for advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンで厳しく指摘して、千紗を\n生まれたての子鹿みたいに震えさせちゃったって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "that she pointed out harshly in the lesson\nand made Chisa tremble like a newborn fawn…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "ひ、酷いです～！　そ、それは、怜ちゃんは厳しいから\nびくびくしちゃうこともありますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's terrible~!　Well‚ that's because Rei-chan is so strict.\nSometimes I get scared…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "それは本気で私と向き合ってくれてるからだって\nちゃんと分かってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know\nit's because she's serious about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.41,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "だから怜ちゃんのハードなレッスンも\n嫌だとは思ってません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I don't mind\nRei-chan's hard lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1466666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "それに、意味なく厳しい訳じゃないんです\nダンスが苦手な私に根気よく付き合ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I'm not being harsh for no reason.\nI'm not a good dancer‚ and she patiently worked with me…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "質問したら丁寧に教えてくれて……\nみんなが踊りやすいように気を配ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I asked her a question‚ she was very polite and helpful. ……\nShe took care to make it easy for everyone to dance. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は怜のことをよく見てるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa knows Rei well‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんだけじゃないです……\nサニピのみんなのことはいつも見てます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan is not the only one……\nI'm always looking out for everyone in Sunny Peace……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、雫ちゃん、遙子さん、怜ちゃん……\n私はみんなに助けられてばかりだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ Shizuku-chan‚ Haruko-san and Rei-chan……\nI'm constantly being helped by everyone…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "いつか私も、みんなを助けられるようになれたらって\n思ってるんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm hoping that someday I'll be able\nto help people‚ too. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "案外みんなも、いつも千紗に助けられてるって\n思ってるかもしれないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You might be surprised to find out that everyone thinks\nChisa is always helping out‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないです……私なんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. …… I'm not ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　橋本さんから電話だ\nもしもし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… hmm?　Hashimoto-san's on the phone.\nHello ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 138.1666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3766.666666600003,
          "startTime": 141.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 144.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "まいったな……\nまさか怜がリハーサル中に足を痛めるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my……\nI never thought Rei would hurt her leg during rehearsal…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんは大丈夫なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is Rei-chan okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "病院で診てもらったが\nちょっと足をひねっただけで大した怪我じゃないそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was checked out at the hospital‚ but they said\nshe just twisted his leg a little and it wasn't a serious injury.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……\nじゃあ、今度のライブには出られるんですね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good……\nSo she will be at the upcoming concert?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そのことなんだが……ダンスをする時は\n激しい動きは避けるようにと医者から言われたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About that‚ …… her doctor told me\nto avoid strenuous movements when dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.8333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　でも今度のライブでは\n怜ちゃんがソロで踊るパートがありますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?　But in the upcoming live performance‚\nRei-chan will have a solo dancing part‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "ソロパートの振り付けは動きが激しくて\n技術的にも難しいから、怜ちゃんじゃないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The choreography for the solo part is technically difficult\nbecause of the intense movement‚ so if it's not Rei-chan‚ it's not ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
