      "text": "もちろんそんなことはさせない\nライブまでに怜を説得するつもりだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I won't let that happen.\nI'm going to try to convince Rei before the concert. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "これでライブバトルに負けたりしたら\n怜ちゃんはきっと悔しがりますよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we lose in the live battle now…\nRei-chan will definitely feel frustrated‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.9533333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "自分のせいだって責任を感じちゃいますよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She'll blame herself for it‚ won't she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
