      "text": "悔しい気持ちは俺も同じだ\nソロパートは見せ場なのに、今から変更するなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel the same frustration.\nIt's a highlight for the solo part‚ and now we're changing it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "だが怪我をした怜に無理をさせる訳にはいかない\n代役がいない以上、振り付けを変えるしかないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we can't force Rei‚ who's injured‚ to do something she can't handle.\nSince there's no substitute‚ we have no choice but to change the choreography.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんの代役……\nあの、{user}さん……私が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan's substitute…\nUm‚ {user}…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "あ……いえ、すみません……なんでもないです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… never mind‚ sorry… it's nothing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
