      "text": "怜ちゃんがやるはずだったソロパートを\n私にやらせてもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could you let me do the solo part that\nRei-chan was supposed to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "難しい振り付けですけど\n頑張って特訓して踊れるようになってみせますから",
