      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "私もやっと体力がついてきて\nダンスも上達したって言われるようになってきて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've finally gained enough stamina and\nthey say my dancing has improved…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs029.m4a",
      "text": "でも、やっぱり自分に自信が持てなくて……\nみんなの足を引っ張ってるんじゃないかと不安で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I still lack confidence in myself…\nI'm worried that I'm holding everyone back…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs030.m4a",
      "text": "私はみんなに追いつきたいんです……私にも出来るって\n胸を張って言えるようになりたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to catch up with everyone…\nI want to be able to say with pride that I can do it too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 309.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs031.m4a",
      "text": "お願いします！　私に挑戦させて下さい！\nこれをやり遂げたら、きっと自信になると思うから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ let me take on this challenge!\nIf I can accomplish this‚ I'm sure it will give me confidence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 316.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことを思ってたのか……\n分かった、そこまで言うなら怜のかわりにやってみるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that's what you've been thinking…\nAlright‚ if you're saying it that seriously‚ I'll let you try it in Rei's place.",
